    @Namespace(value="nvinfer1::plugin")
 @Properties(inherit=nvinfer_plugin.class)
public class PriorBoxParameters
extends Pointer
    \struct PriorBoxParameters \brief The PriorBox plugin layer generates the prior boxes of designated sizes and aspect ratios across all dimensions (H x W). PriorBoxParameters defines a set of parameters for creating the PriorBox plugin layer.
